s='chitiet_tin'><h2>Radamel Falcao ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Anh vs Colombia, ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Monaco kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Falcao ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nColombia \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i ki\u00ean c\u01b0\u1eddng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Anh, d\u00f9 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u01b0ng h\u1ecd v\u1eabn ki\u00ean c\u01b0\u1eddng t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 \u1edf nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat b\u00f9 gi\u1edd. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 thua 3-4 tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m, qua \u0111\u00f3 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Radamel Falcao ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Anh vs Colombia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Radamel Falcao ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Anh vs Colombia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/4/falcao-cay-cu-anh-chien-thang-vi-trong-tai.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Falcao n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Anh vs Colombia</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i \u0111\u00e3 r\u00fat ra t\u1edbi 8 th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng, 6 trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 Colombia. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u li\u00ean t\u1ee5c b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ee9t qu\u00e3ng b\u1edfi nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i.&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd ph\u1ea3i k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng Wilmar Barrios h\u00fac v\u00e0o ng\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a Henderson, r\u1ea5t may l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 mang \u00e1o s\u1ed1 5 c\u1ee7a Colombia ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nRadamel Falcao ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Anh vs Colombia, ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Monaco kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;\u00d4ng \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra nhi\u1ec1u quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i cho ch\u00fang t\u00f4i, t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng th\u1ed5i ph\u1ea1t 11m kh\u00f4ng r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng tranh ch\u1ea5p b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng. Trong nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng 50-50 \u00f4ng \u1ea5y \u0111\u1ec1u cho Anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;\u00d4ng \u1ea5y l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi M\u1ef9, \u00f4ng \u1ea5y n\u00f3i ti\u1ebfng Anh, \u00f4ng \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i cho Anh. Tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i khi\u1ebfn ch\u00fang t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i \u1ee9c ch\u1ebf, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Colombia. Th\u1eadt \u0111\u00e1ng x\u1ea5u h\u1ed5 khi t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng n\u00e0y x\u1ea3y ra \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Falcao khen ng\u1ee3i tinh th\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Colombia</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 Colombia kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc Anh, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Falcao v\u1eabn \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao tinh th\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Falcao can chung to truoc DT Anh\" title=\"Falcao c\u1ea7n ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T Anh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/gap-dt-anh-la-co-hoi-de-falcao-chung-to-minh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Falcao khen ng\u1ee3i tinh th\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, Colombia \u0111\u00e3 chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng gi\u00e2y ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng. T\u00f4i h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. H\u00f4m nay, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c m\u00ecnh, Colombia x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;Anh \u0111\u00e3 may m\u1eafn h\u01a1n tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m \u0111\u1ea7y may r\u1ee7i. H\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Colombia \u1edf World Cup 2018 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"894","checkdouble":"190363"},{"date":"15:32 04/07","title":"Lingard: \"Anh \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i ng\u00e0y n\u00e0y r\u1ea5t l\u00e2u r\u1ed3i\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/4/lingard-anh-da-cho-doi-ngay-nay-rat-lau-roi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Jesse Lingard ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 mu\u1ed1n c\u00f9ng Tam s\u01b0 l\u00e0m n\u00ean l\u1ecbch s\u1eed \u1edf World Cup 2018.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Anh \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft World Cup 2018</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAnh \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t \u1edf World Cup 2018, h\u1ecd d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 2 b\u1ea3ng G. Vi\u1ec7c x\u1ebfp \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 2 sau B\u1ec9 gi\u00fap Tam s\u01b0 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o nh\u00e1nh thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jesse Lingard ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Jesse Lingard ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/4/Jesse-Lingard-phat-bieu-ve-DT-Anh-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Anh \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Colombia tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede v\u00f2ng 1/8, Harry Kane v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Colombia. \u0110\u00fang nh\u01b0 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n, tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra r\u1ea5t h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn v\u00e0 c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng. Hai \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00f2a nhau 1-1 sau 120 ph\u00fat, tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m Tam s\u01b0 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 4-3.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/truc-tiep-anh-vs-colombia-463-190303.html\" target=\"_blank\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Anh vs Colombia</span> gi\u00fap Tam s\u01b0 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n. N\u1ebfu gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y S\u01b0 t\u1eed anh s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Croatia ho\u1eb7c Nga \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft \u0111ang r\u1ed9ng m\u1edf v\u1edbi Anh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong tay HLV Gareth Southgate \u0111ang s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t d\u00e0n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng, ngo\u00e0i ra Anh c\u00f2n nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a may m\u1eafn. Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft v\u00e0 l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch l\u00e0 chuy\u1ec7n ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Jesse Lingard mu\u1ed1n c\u00f9ng Anh l\u00e0m n\u00ean l\u1ecbch s\u1eed</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Jesse Lingard ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 mu\u1ed1n c\u00f9ng Tam s\u01b0 l\u00e0m n\u00ean l\u1ecbch s\u1eed \u1edf World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lingard phat bieu ve DT Anh\" title=\"Lingard ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/4/lingard-anh-da-cho-doi-ngay-nay-rat-lau-roi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Lingard ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110\u00e3 l\u00e2u l\u1eafm r\u1ed3i ch\u00fang t\u00f4i m\u1edbi l\u1ea1i l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup, tuy nhi\u00ean ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u01b0a mu\u1ed1n d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i. Anh mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111i s\u00e2u \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch, Anh \u0111\u1ee7 s\u1ee9c l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cNHM \u0111ang \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn v\u00e0o ch\u00fang t\u00f4i, to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u1ee5 s\u1ef1 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng n\u01a1i NHM. Anh \u0111ang r\u1ea5t th\u0103ng hoa sau nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i h\u1ea1 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng cao chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"893","checkdouble":"190364"},{"date":"15:16 04/07","title":"\u0110\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 r\u1eddi World Cup, L\u0110B\u0110 T\u00e2y Ban Nha ch\u1ed1t 3 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean thay th\u1ebf HLV Hierro","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/2/cay-dang-roi-world-cup-ldbd-tay-ban-nha-chot-3-ung-vien-thay-the-hlv-hierro.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo ngu\u1ed3n tin t\u1eeb L\u0110B\u0110 Vi\u1ec7t Nam, \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd tham d\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u T\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng do VFF t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh t\u1edbi t\u1eeb 3 n\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c l\u00e0 Uzbekistan, Australia v\u00e0 Oman.</h2><h2>U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ee5ng to\u00e0n 'h\u00e0ng kh\u1ee7ng' tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m ASIAD 2018\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><em><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ee5ng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1ng g\u1eddm tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m ASIAD 2018  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ee5ng to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1ng g\u1eddm tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m ASIAD 2018  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/1/29/DT-U23-Viet-Nam-dung-toan-doi-thu-dang-gom-truoc-them-ASIAD-2018--hinh-anh.jpg\"></em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i \u0110T U23 Uzbekistan\u00a0tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m ASIAD 2018\u00a0</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018 di\u1ec5n ra tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Trung Qu\u1ed1c h\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m nay, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u0103ng hoa t\u1ea1i k\u1ef3 \u00c1 v\u1eadn h\u1ed9i ASIAD 2018 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 8 t\u1edbi t\u1ea1i Indonesia.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eb1m gi\u00fap \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1edbi n\u00f2ng c\u1ed1t v\u1eabn l\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U23 b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i tr\u00ean 23 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho ASIAD s\u1eafp t\u1edbi, m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y L\u0110B\u0110 Vi\u1ec7t Nam VFF \u0111\u00e3 li\u00ean h\u1ec7 t\u1edbi c\u00e1c L\u0110B\u0110 t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c1 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm qu\u00e2n xanh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n. V\u00e0 3 c\u00e1i t\u00ean nh\u1eadn l\u1eddi tham d\u1ef1 l\u00e0 \u0110T Olympic \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb Uzbekistan, Australia v\u00e0 Oman.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, l\u1ee9a C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Quang H\u1ea3i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i g\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1eebng kho\u00e1c \u00e1o U23 Uzbekistan \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1. Ngo\u00e0i ra, c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i \u00dac, Oman c\u0169ng l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1ng g\u1eddm cho th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo \u2018m\u00e0i g\u01b0\u01a1m\u2019 tr\u00ean h\u00e0nh tr\u00ecnh chinh ph\u1ee5c t\u1ea5m huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng ASIAD v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 8 t\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin b\u00ean l\u1ec1, gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra trong 3 ng\u00e0y m\u00f9ng 3, 5 v\u00e0 7/8 t\u1edbi t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9 \u0110\u00ecnh. Gi\u00e1 v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c BTC gi\u1ea3i c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 t\u1eeb 150.000 \u0111\u1ed3ng, 200.000 \u0111\u1ed3ng, 300.000 \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u00e0 cao nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 400.000 \u0111\u1ed3ng t\u00f9y khu v\u1ef1c. M\u1ed7i v\u00e9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xem \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u trong c\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y thi \u0111\u1ea5u.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n s\u1ebd c\u00f2n kho\u1ea3ng g\u1ea7n n\u1eeda th\u00e1ng luy\u1ec7n t\u1eadp tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tranh t\u00e0i \u1edf ASIAD 2018 s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ea1i Jakarta, Indonesia t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 18/8 t\u1edbi.\u00a0<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/dt-olympic-viet-nam-gap-bat-loi-khi-bi-xep-vao-nhom-hat-giong-thap-tai-asiad-168-189648.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/dt-olympic-viet-nam-gap-bat-loi-khi-bi-xep-vao-nhom-hat-giong-thap-tai-asiad.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/dt-olympic-viet-nam-gap-bat-loi-khi-bi-xep-vao-nhom-hat-giong-thap-tai-asiad-168-189648.html\">\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam g\u1eb7p b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i khi b\u1ecb x\u1ebfp v\u00e0o nh\u00f3m h\u1ea1t gi\u1ed1ng th\u1ea5p t\u1ea1i ASIAD</span><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, H\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed3ng Olympic ch\u00e2u \u00c1 (OCA) \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 nh\u00f3m h\u1ea1t gi\u1ed1ng c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 th\u1eddi gian b\u1ed1c th\u0103m chia b\u1ea3ng m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018....</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/goc-nhin-thay-park-se-cham-van-lam-hay-bui-tien-dung-cho-asiad-2018-168-187794.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/5/goc-nhin-thay-park-se-cham-van-lam-hay-bui-tien-dung-cho-asiad-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/goc-nhin-thay-park-se-cham-van-lam-hay-bui-tien-dung-cho-asiad-2018-168-187794.html\">G\u00f3c nh\u00ecn: Th\u1ea7y Park s\u1ebd ch\u1ea5m V\u0103n L\u00e2m hay B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng cho ASIAD 2018?</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m v\u00e0 B\u00f9i Ti\u1ebfn D\u0169ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 hai th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n thi \u0111\u1ea5u n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Nh\u01b0ng li\u1ec7u HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd ch\u1ecdn ai b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh cho \u0110T Olympic...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/van-lam-anh-duc-va-nhung-guong-mat-nao-co-the-tham-du-asiad-2018-168-183020.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/28/van-lam-anh-duc-va-nhung-guong-mat-nao-co-the-tham-du-asiad-2018.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/van-lam-anh-duc-va-nhung-guong-mat-nao-co-the-tham-du-asiad-2018-168-183020.html\">V\u0103n L\u00e2m, Anh \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t n\u00e0o c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tham d\u1ef1 Asiad 2018?</span><br>\r\nTr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 Jordan v\u1eeba qua ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 HLV Park Hang Seo ki\u1ec3m nghi\u1ec7m l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 qua \u0111\u00f3 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi Asiad 2018 v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau chinh ph\u1ee5c danh...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nguyen-tien-linh-manh-ghep-con-thieu-cua-thay-park-168-187368.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/30/nguyen-tien-linh-manh-ghep-con-thieu-cua-thay-park.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nguyen-tien-linh-manh-ghep-con-thieu-cua-thay-park-168-187368.html\">Nguy\u1ec5n Ti\u1ebfn Linh: M\u1ea3nh gh\u00e9p c\u00f2n thi\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y Park?</span><br>\r\n\u0110i v\u00e0o l\u1ecbch s\u1eed v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb tu\u1ed5i nh\u1ea5t t\u1ea1o m\u1ed9t c\u00fa poker b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u1ea1i V-League, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o tr\u1ebb Nguy\u1ec5n Ti\u1ebfn Linh \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u l\u1eddi khen t\u1eeb gi\u1edbi...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"892","checkdouble":"190365"},{"date":"15:38 04/07","title":"\u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i sau VCK World Cup 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/4/da-co-nha-cam-quan-dau-tien-bi-sa-thai-sau-vck-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Qu\u00e1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 t\u1ea1i VCK World Cup 2018, \u200bLi\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ba Lan v\u1eeba m\u1edbi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh sa th\u1ea3i hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T Ba Lan, Adam Nawa\u0142ka.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify; \">L\u0110B\u0110 Ba Lan sa th\u1ea3i HLV Adam Nawa\u0142ka sau World Cup 2018&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Adam Nawa\u0142ka Ba Lan tai World Cup 2018\" title=\"HLV Adam Nawa\u0142ka Ba Lan t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/7/balan.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Adam Nawa\u0142ka b\u1ecb L\u0110B\u0110 Ba Lan sa th\u1ea3i sau World Cup 2018</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u1ebfp v\u00e0o nh\u00f3m h\u1ea1t gi\u1ed1ng s\u1ed1 1 t\u1ea1i VCK World Cup l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y tuy nhi\u00ean \u0110T Ba Lan \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i s\u1edbm ch\u1ec9 sau 2 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc Senegal v\u00e0 Colombia. Ba Lan ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng danh d\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i song \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u00f4ng Adam Nawa\u0142ka t\u1ea1i v\u1ecb tr\u00ean chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng \u1edf \u0110T Ba Lan sau gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, L\u0110B\u0110 Ban Lan \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0a ra th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o sa th\u1ea3i HLV Adam Nawa\u0142ka v\u00ec th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ngh\u00e8o n\u00e0n \u1edf VCK World Cup l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y. Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 li\u00ean quan t\u1edbi v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n,&nbsp;Adam Nawalka c\u00f2n b\u1ecb c\u00e1o bu\u1ed9c r\u1eb1ng thi\u00ean v\u1ecb nhi\u1ec1u ng\u00f4i sao trong \u0110T Ba Lan, ti\u00eau bi\u1ec3u nh\u01b0&nbsp;Robert Lewandowski, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ec3 nhi\u1ec1u tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 ti\u1ec7c t\u00f9ng ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc ng\u00e0y l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng sang Nga thi \u0111\u1ea5u, c\u00f9ng nhi\u1ec1u c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n l\u00f9m x\u00f9m h\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00e1c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o sa th\u1ea3i HLV Adam Nawa\u0142ka c\u00f3 \u0111o\u1ea1n: &ldquo;L\u0110B\u0110 Ba Lan \u0111\u00e3 \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eb1ng Adam Nawalka s\u1ebd l\u00e0 HLV tuy\u1ec3n Ba Lan cho \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ebft ng\u00e0y 30/7. Sau th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t HLV m\u1edbi. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n theo h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111i m\u1edbi&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c b\u1ecb th\u1ea5t nghi\u1ec7p sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0110T Ba Lan tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga, HLV Adam Nawa\u0142ka \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh v\u1ecb HLV \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean b\u1ecb sa th\u1ea3i sau World Cup. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a HLV Nawa\u0142ka, \u00f4ng Hector Cuper, HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T Ai C\u1eadp c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 n\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00e0y sau World Cup 2018, tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 do ph\u00eda L\u0110B\u0110 Ai C\u1eadp kh\u00f4ng ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n Argentina n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-ba-lan-vs-nhat-ban-461-189884.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/clip-ban-thang-ba-lan-vs-nhat-ban.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-ba-lan-vs-nhat-ban-461-189884.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n 0-1 Ba Lan (B\u1ea3ng H World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nD\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c song \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n x\u1ee9 m\u1eb7t tr\u1eddi m\u1ecdc v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ba Lan \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i. May m\u1eafn thay, t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp v\u1eabn thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 h\u1ecd.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/dau-la-nguyen-nhan-khien-dt-ba-lan-tham-bai-truoc-colombia-421-189472.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/25/dau-la-nguyen-nhan-khien-dt-ba-lan-tham-bai-truoc-colombia.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/dau-la-nguyen-nhan-khien-dt-ba-lan-tham-bai-truoc-colombia-421-189472.html\">\u0110\u00e2u l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n khi\u1ebfn \u0110T Ba Lan th\u1ea3m b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Colombia?</span><br>\r\nT\u1ea1i Kazan Arena t\u1ed1i 24/6, \u0110T Ba Lan \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i cay \u0111\u1eafng 0-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Colombia trong th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn thua k\u00e9m \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. V\u1eady \u0111\u00e2u l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n d\u1eabn t\u1edbi th\u1ea5t...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-ba-lan-vs-colombia-461-189465.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/25/clip-ban-thang-ba-lan-vs-colombia.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-ba-lan-vs-colombia-461-189465.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Ba Lan 0-3 Colombia (B\u1ea3ng H World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nNh\u1edd 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Yerri Mina, Radamel Falcao v\u00e0 Juan Cuadrado, Colombia \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Ba Lan v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 3-0 \u0111\u1ec3 nhen nh\u00f3m hy v\u1ecdng \u0111i ti\u1ebfp, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi ti\u1ec5n...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"891","checkdouble":"190366"},{"date":"16:35 04/07","title":"Southgate: \"\u0110T Anh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ecbch s\u1eed ng\u00e1ng ch\u00e2n m\u00ecnh\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/4/southgate-dt-anh-khong-the-de-lich-su-ngang-chan-minh.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Gareth Southgate kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ecbch s\u1eed c\u1ea3n b\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00ecnh sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Colombia tr\u00ean lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m \u0111\u00eam qua.</h2><h2>\u0110\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh ph\u00e1 r\u00e0o c\u1ea3n l\u1ecbch s\u1eed</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tam S\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf lo\u1ea1t s\u00fat lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i World Cup v\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam qua. Eric Dier l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u00fa s\u00fat quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh sau khi Jordan Pickford t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Bacca tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nV\u00e0 sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV Southgate kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean b\u1ecb y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 l\u1ecbch s\u1eed t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng. B\u1edfi v\u00ec h\u1ecd \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i t\u1ef1 vi\u1ebft ra nh\u1eefng trang s\u1eed m\u1edbi \u1edf <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018-c421-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">World Cup 2018</span> n\u00e0y.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Southgate mu\u1ed1n \u0110T Anh vi\u1ebft n\u00ean l\u1ecbch s\u1eed \u1edf World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Southgate mu\u1ed1n \u0110T Anh vi\u1ebft n\u00ean l\u1ecbch s\u1eed \u1edf World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/4/southgate-dt-anh-khong-the-de-lich-su-ngang-chan-minh.JPG\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Southgate mu\u1ed1n \u0110T\u00a0Anh vi\u1ebft n\u00ean l\u1ecbch s\u1eed \u1edf World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<em>\u201cT\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd qu\u00ean c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 tr\u01b0\u1ee3t penalty \u0111\u00f3 (\u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p \u0110\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i Euro 1996). Th\u1eadt bu\u1ed3n khi \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc s\u1ebd \u0111i c\u00f9ng t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ebft \u0111\u1eddi.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n\u201cNh\u01b0ng h\u00f4m nay, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t. V\u00e0 t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng r\u1eb1ng n\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc t\u1ea1o c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng cho c\u00e1c th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ti\u1ebfp theo. B\u1edfi v\u00ec h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ea5y r\u1eb1ng b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n\u201cTrong cu\u1ed9c s\u1ed1ng, b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ecbch s\u1eed c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng c\u1ea3n b\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00ecnh. C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n Anh \u0111ang th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. H\u1ecd t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 \u0111ang chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft s\u1eafp t\u1edbi\u201d.</em></div>\r\n<h2>Southgate khen ng\u1ee3i Pickford</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Pickford l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n Anh d\u00f9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Everton m\u1edbi ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1 khi \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi b\u00e0n thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9. Nh\u01b0ng m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, HLV Southgate \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i v\u00ec nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ee9u thua xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc tr\u01b0\u1edbc Colombia.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<em>\u201cT\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 c\u00fa s\u00fat xa c\u1ee7a Muriel l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t pha c\u1ee9u thua \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. T\u00f4i c\u0169ng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00f3ng d\u00f9 chi\u1ec1u cao kh\u00e1 khi\u00eam t\u1ed1n.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t khu v\u1ef1c c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t. V\u00e0 Pickford c\u00f2n th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i trong lo\u1ea1t s\u00fat lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u00fat penalty c\u1ee7a Colombia. V\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1eeba qua c\u00f3 c\u00f4ng l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a Pickford c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ed9i ng\u0169 c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i khi chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u th\u00f4ng tin h\u1eefu \u00edch tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i khi n\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1eddi c\u0169ng mang l\u1ea1i cho b\u1ea1n nh\u1eefng g\u00ec b\u1ea1n x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. Nh\u01b0ng h\u00f4m nay, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u1edbi n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c b\u1ecf ra\u201d.</em><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng l\u1ecbch s\u1eed c\u1ee7a \u0110T\u00a0Anh:</strong><br />\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/colombia-vs-anh-01-tieu-xao-sai-lam-va-nhung-dac-trung-lam-nen-tran-cau-sieu-kich-tinh-421-190343.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m Colombia 1-1 (pen 3-4) Anh: Ti\u1ec3u x\u1ea3o, sai l\u1ea7m v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1eb7c tr\u01b0ng l\u00e0m n\u00ean tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u si\u00eau k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/thay-gi-sau-dem-lich-su-sang-trang-cho-nguoi-anh-tren-cham-11m-421-190321.html\">Th\u1ea5y g\u00ec sau \u0111\u00eam l\u1ecbch s\u1eed sang trang cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"890","checkdouble":"190367"}]}